product.shortDescription: Mr. Clean’s 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner muscles through 100% of dirt and grease for powerful, multi-surface cleaning. This floor cleaner for mopping is great for cleaning linoleum, tile & hardwood floors**. Use Mr. Clean’s 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner as a bathroom cleaner to clean toilets, sinks, and bathtubs. This multi-surface cleaner even works outside on garbage cans, doors, and more. It makes cleaning your house that much easier and leaves the long-lasting freshness of Febreze Meadows & Rain scent behind. Add Mr. Clean’s 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner to your arsenal of cleaning supplies today! *vs. Mr. Clean Original **use diluted only. This product is a great addition to your cleaning supplies, ensuring effective and efficient cleaning.
product.name: Mr. Clean 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner, Febreze Meadows & Rain Scent, 41 fl oz

fulfillmentLabel.message: Shipping, arrives by tomorrow to Westwood, 41101

directions.name: Instructions
directions.value: FLOORS/DILUTE CLEANING: Mix 1/8 cup per 1 gallon (1/2 bucket) of water. Usually no need to rinse. TOUGH JOBS: Pour directly on tough soil or on sponge. Wipe and rinse. **FINISHED WOOD: Use diluted only. Not recommended for carpets, copper or aluminum surfaces. If applied to stainless steel wipe dry immediately. Rinse hands after use. *A rinse is required for surfaces in direct contact with food. Not for use on food contact surfaces including dishes, glassware, cookware and utensils.

idml.longDescription:
• Get a powerful clean and a great scent with Mr. Clean’s 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner with Febreze Meadows & Rain scent. It cuts through 100% of dirt, grease, and grime, leaving the scent of Meadows & Rain liquid cleaner in its dirt-forsaken place.
  • Mr. Clean’s 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner works all around the house! Use on everything from linoleum, to tile and finished hardwood floors, to toilets and bathtubs, and even garbage cans.
  • Cuts through 100% of dirt, grease and grime
  • Great for use on sinks, counters, stoves and more!
  • Mr. Clean’s 2X Concentrated Multi Surface, All Purpose Cleaner is also available in Unstopables Fresh, Gain Original Fresh, Lavender and Lemon
  • Fresh scent of Meadows & Rain
  • 41 fl oz
  • A great addition to your cleaning supplies for effective and efficient cleaning

reviewSummary.summary: Customers highly praise Mr. Clean Multi-Surface Cleaner with Febreze Meadows and Rain for its affordability, ease of use, and effectiveness on various floors, leaving them clean, shiny, and fresh-smelling without residue or streaks. The concentrated formula provides great value, longevity, and a pleasant, fresh smell that lasts. Overall, customers appreciate the product's simplicity, quality, and economical cost, making it a remarkable purchase.
reviewSummary.summaryTitle: Effective and affordable multi-surface cleaner for fresh and clean floors

bulletSummaryAspects.aspectSummary: Leaves surfaces clean without residue or film.
Cleans floors without residue or streaks.
Leaves a pleasant aroma after use.
Simple to operate for various cleaning tasks.
Offers good value for its performance.

customerReviews.reviewText: I love Mr clean. I've always used it and was afraid that it had disappeared from the shelves until they repackaged it. It works extremely well and you don't need very much. I run an Airbnb and I have plank flooring on all the floors. A little bit of that into a hot wash of water really gets things clean. And the rooms smell great. We always get five stars and I think Mr clean is one of the reasons

It's a good product, I've been using it for years . Being I have chronic. sinuses I like that this scent is not strong the fumes don't bother me. I can handle it when I'm cleaning and it leaves my house smelling nice and fresh.

Our go to product for cleaning and disinfecting. Incredible results. Perfect from kitchen, bath,floors, walls and outside too! Siding, RV Cleaning. Works great on the awning. We've used this for years and continue to be thoroughly impressed. The scent is lovely. Fresh and clean.  Highly Recommended.
I love the smell and the cleanliness of this product. I use it for everything in my home including kitchen appliances, bathroom fixtures, walls as well as floors.

It's one of my favorite things in this scent and other scents! And it's one you can actually tell it's more concentrated and that's the first time I've actually seen proof from general usage over the years! Oh I love this product and I'm so many scents! %231 👌🔥👑🫶💙🩵💙🩵♾️♾️♾️♾️
customerReviews.reviewTitle: The Best all purpose cleaner ever in my opinion!

customerReviews.reviewText: I really   like Mr.  Clean and have another issue with another product that I can't seem to get anyone to look into.. I ordered a jar of beets a month ago today and says delayed and says it is at the post office in New York and pending. so where is it?

Very good price, and large size is better price. This cleaner works well in the kitchen, on counters, sinks and stainless-steel appliances, not harsh, does not scratch and smells wonderful. I have tile floors, and Mr. Clean 2X   also works well on different flooring.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: Mr.Clean works for all my cleaning needs.

customerReviews.reviewText: Our absolute favorite floor cleaner.  It smells clean without feeling bleach-y and just generally does a fantastic job.  We use this on our brick floors in our old Southwest Adobe home and have had no issues with it damaging our floors, which is always a concern in maintaining of an old historic home.

Oh my gosh! Where do I start? Obviously this has great cleaning power because it's Mr. Clean, but oh my, the scent of this cleaner is so perfect!!! Sometimes the fragrance from cleaning products disappears very quickly, but not this! This is the best scent I've found from any cleaning agent! After 3 days of using this, my house still remains with a light, fresh, and delightful smell. That says a lot for a family of 4 with 2 dogs and 3 cats! Keep it up Mr. Clean! Well done!!

I don't like ordering items from Walmart that are sold by other vendors and the items are not available for two weeks.  Sometimes the item will be shipped later and I don't need the item any longer.  I have no way of knowing if the item was charged to my account or not.  I contact Walmart and they tell me to contact the seller.
customerReviews.reviewTitle: Items that are not available when I place an order

topNegativeReview.reviewText:
The New Formula is absolutely awful- DOES NoT clean dirt for grease. 
User of the old formula for 50 years…
I've tried them all and Mr Clean was always superior.  Customers would like to know the reason for the change to such an inferior product.
I would give it a negative star if that was an option.
Why you would change a perfect product is beyond comprehension- it's all over the internet, how very unhappy people are with the new product.

clientResponses.response: I'm so very sorry to hear that a loyal Mr. Clean user for over 50 years had a cleaner that isn't up to the quality standard that you have come to know, love, and trust. What you experienced isn't what we expect, especially since my team and I have not changed this formula in the US. We'd love to connect and get to the bottom of this. Please call us at (800) 867-2532.
